        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer525837814" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11521006357572438183">Interesting book. Definitely a good explanation of the quantum world. That said, there are also a number of intriguing philosophical questions that arise throughout the book that make any confusion with respect to the physics/math aspects worth the struggle. Overall, a good, quick read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


